RFC 1036 has been changed to RFC822 regarding to §2.1.2</p>

<p>Note: These implementations are following the standard STRICT... this means when the standard defines "implementations should follow old standard because of redundancy" this will not be supported... use ISO_8601 in this case or define the format manually.</p>

